Prevent the device from going to sleep
4. Legal basis
We process your data for the purposes and purposes stated in this privacy policy. The legal basis includes: the processing necessary to perform the contract with you (for example, providing you with the services you request and identifying and verifying your identity); the legal requirements that must be complied with (for example, complying with applicable accounting rules and submitting to law enforcement agencies) Mandatory disclosure); necessary for our legitimate interests (for example, managing our relationship with you, ensuring the safety of our services, communicating with you about our products and services); and based on our customers’ consent (for example, placing Certain cookies also share your information with third parties for advertising purposes).
In some cases, you may need to provide us with personal data for the above processing so that we can provide you with all our services and allow you to use all the functions of our application.
5. Your rights
You need to exercise any rights granted by law. You can contact us by email
support@liuzhosoft.com
, but we may restrict some of your rights due to the following conditions
Does not meet legal requirements
Infringe on other people’s data
Protect our rights and property
The request is meaningless or fragmentary
5.1. Right to withdraw consent
You can stop using our service at any time. When you stop using it, we will immediately stop collecting any of your data.
5.2. Access and correction of personal data
You can ask us to provide a copy of your personal data (this may incur a certain fee within the scope of the law), or you can ask us to correct your personal information. But if this infringes on the privacy or rights of others, we may reject your request.
5.3. Restricted rights
In some cases, you can restrict our processing of your personal data
Our processing is illegal, you object to our actions and restrict our use of your data
You question the accuracy of our data processing
You need to use this information to exercise your legal rights and restrict the use of data
Other legitimate requests
5.4. Make a complaint
If you think we have violated your privacy rights, you can complain to us via email at
support@liuzhosoft.com
, and we will remove your doubts. You also have the right to lodge a complaint with the competent authority of the Member State where you are habitually resident.
5.5. Other undeclared but legal rights
6. Privacy statement of third-party partners
When we adopt a new third-party service, we will update it here in time.
